# Keep this monorepo focused on the RTS project for GitHub sync/release.
*
!.gitignore
!.github/
.github/*
!.github/workflows/
!.github/workflows/**
!2D/
2D/*
!2D/medieval_rts/
!2D/medieval_rts/**

# Project-specific ignores
2D/medieval_rts/.DS_Store
2D/medieval_rts/**/.DS_Store
2D/medieval_rts/**/__pycache__/
2D/medieval_rts/.pytest_cache/
2D/medieval_rts/build/
2D/medieval_rts/dist/
2D/medieval_rts/release/
2D/medieval_rts/replays/*.json
2D/medieval_rts/replays/*.rpl
2D/medieval_rts/*.spec
